## üñ•Ô∏è 3. `systemd/smartcane.service`

Include your service file here so it's version-controlled:

```ini
[Unit]
Description=Smart Cane Navigation System
After=network.target

[Service]
ExecStart=/usr/bin/python3 /home/pi/smart-cane/main.py
WorkingDirectory=/home/pi/smart-cane
Restart=always
User=pi

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
